@andrew-bushnell Transparency has always been at the core of our culture.

In addition to the bi-weekly company updates that we are currently publishing for our Republic campaign, we have also been publishing regular updates on our blog for our userbase for the past two years: blog.bounty0x.io

Our investors can definitely expect updates to continue even after the campaign, both on our company blog and on social media (mainly Twitter).

@baron-huntington Currently, the only way for a regular individual to get involved in crypto is by *buying* cryptocurrencies.

This creates several challenges and comes with risks that many people are not willing to take.

At Bounty0x we solve this problem by offering an alternative: instead of having to buy crypto, we enable anyone to get some coins by earning them.
